--Real Proof of Concept exploit--

You can see that the /etc/passwd is readed two times and a lot more if we don't stop the script execution.

- How to fix it? More information?
--------------------------------------------------------
Like the Hardened-PHP staff said, you have to disallow the use of symlink() function.
You can do this using the disable_functions directive in your php configuration (php.ini by default):

disable_functions = ...,symlink;

